cdata.name: CryptoForecast
cdata.desc: Cryptoforecast is a trading/invesment tool build both for new and experienced users. It helpsusersidentifythe inversions of trend and ride them from the beginning. This is done through the use of the forecast PILLAR algorithm, which isconstantly evolvng, being able to adapt to new markets and in different time frames for any type of trading and at the same time adapting to the characteristics of each Trader.CFT is a token issued on the Bitcoin blockchain through the OMNI Layer. This token allows users to subscribe to the platform.
